assets.name: assets/dyAWWtu0q2Y
assets.description:
Who's gonna win?? Left Swan or Right Swan. 

Left Swan looks locked in and determined to win. We all remember what happened last time. 

Right Swan has been waiting for this day for weeks. Practicing in mirrors and glass windows, looks ready to go. 

You couldn't cut this tension with a knife. These swans give everything,  as they always do, to try and win.
